PASTEURELLA PNEUMONIA, BIG HORN SHEEP - USA (5)
================================================

Martin Hugh-Jones wrote:
>
> From: MATSON@PICARD.EVMS.EDU

> Date: Mon, 29 Jan 1996 09:09:03 -0400 (EDT)
